      "rationale": "Formal use error assessment is not required at MRL 2. Simulation activities were conducted by a PhD-level engineer with 8 years of CFD experience in cardiovascular devices. A peer review of boundary condition setup and post-processing procedures was completed prior to production runs."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
