      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; correspondence between simulation and experimental inputs is documented qualitatively.",
      "rationale": "Simulation boundary conditions were set to match experimental test conditions. Formal equivalency analysis between in vitro and in silico input parameters is not required at MRL 2. Qualitative correspondence is documented in the simulation protocol."
